{"tid":778816,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普簽署國防授權法　部分內容涉強化台灣軍力戰備","createTime":"2018-08-14T03:24:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T00:26:43.000Z","uid":79563,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0b538c5e52136fe7faa4460fab9159876ce8a49e","tid":778816,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T03:24:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1412267_1_L_20180814103839.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1412267_1_L_20180814103839.jpg&h=b1b436e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1412267-20180814.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1412267-20180814.htm&d=8wRfes4BNiqzHQc1cLrktvjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=98ffddbf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1412267-20180814.htm&h=c036a29f\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1412267-20180814.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普簽署「2019財政年度國防授權法」，這項由參眾兩院通過的法案正式生效，五角大廈獲得預算7160億美元。<br />\n<br />\n法案中提到，要強化台灣軍力戰備，包括美國國防部長與適當的台灣官員諮商後，必須全面評估台灣軍力，尤其是台灣的後備軍力，並在法案生效開始的一年內，經與國務卿諮商，向國會的適當委員會提出評估報告。<br />\n<br />\n美國國會的意見又認為，美國國防部長應推動國防部的交流政策，強化台灣安全，包括推動與台灣進行實戰訓練及軍演的機會；依據「台灣旅行法」推動美台資深防衛官員及軍事將領交流。"},{"pid":"d4208749f9c755dfa1a570dde4f573752cb7bbca","tid":778816,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T13:43:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54148fa4c1cd9b44d5ea040b5fc28ff87686a3b3","tid":778816,"uid":55628,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T13:45:24.000Z","msg":"若言屬實，中国或成為最大贏家。"},{"pid":"e937e07292c6d45423d5e3936807b7dbfd87034e","tid":778816,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T13:48:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\